**/.env
**/.env.
!**/.env.example
**/vw-data/
**/letsencrypt/

# Service data and config directories (contain runtime state/secrets)
**/data/
docker/homeassistant/config/
docker/traefik/certs/

# Cloudflared — tunnel credentials and resolved config (contain tunnel ID and secrets)
docker/cloudflared/*.json
docker/cloudflared/cert.pem
docker/cloudflared/config.yml

# TLS private keys
**/*-key.pem

# OpenCode - Sensitive authentication files (antigravity)
**/antigravity-accounts.json
**/antigravity-signature-cache.json
**/antigravity-logs/

# OpenCode - Additional sensitive data patterns (defense-in-depth)
**/opencode/auth.json
**/opencode/storage/
**/opencode/log/
**/opencode/snapshot/
**/opencode/tool-output/
